Company Summary
ARRIS International plc is an IP, video and broadband technology company. The Company offers video infrastructure, delivery networks, home and business connectivity and devices as well as related products. ARRIS International plc, formerly known as ARRIS GROUP INC, is based in Suwanee, United States.   





 



 

